WEBVTT

00:09:58.221 --> 00:10:00.751
He said, "You listened.

00:10:00.751 --> 00:10:05.951
You let me speak, and you just listened."

00:10:05.951 --> 00:10:07.910
Shortly after this incident,

00:10:07.910 --> 00:10:11.169
I received a letter from Kevin's mother,

00:10:11.169 --> 00:10:14.081
and I have that letter with me,

00:10:14.081 --> 00:10:16.931
and I'd like to read it to you.

00:10:16.931 --> 00:10:19.087
"Dear Mr. Briggs,

00:10:19.087 --> 00:10:21.952
Nothing will erase the events of March 11,

00:10:21.952 --> 00:10:25.080
but you are one of the reasons Kevin is still with us.

00:10:25.080 --> 00:10:29.373
I truly believe Kevin was crying out for help.

00:10:29.373 --> 00:10:32.095
He has been diagnosed with a mental illness